URL: http://github.com/lillem4n/kohana-module-pajas

The pajas module is a collection of tools and extensions to Kohana.

It is compatible with version 3.0.x

Parts of the pajas project is also stand alone projects:
PDO  - http://github.com/lillem4n/kohana-module-pdo
XML  - http://github.com/lillem4n/kohana-module-xml
XSLT - http://github.com/lillem4n/kohana-module-xslt
